reviews.review_text: I came here looking for some fresh seafood and boy did I find a gem. The service was fantastic and the staff is very knowledgeable, the product are extremely fresh and of amazing quality. The store is kept very clean and I would highly recommend and come back to buy more. Keep up the great work guys
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the great review Stanley!

reviews.review_text: I came in and bought 2 lbs of fresh prawns($63). The man at the counter was helpful and polite. The prawns were absolutely delicious! If you ever need some good seafood to impress people at a party, this is the place to buy from.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: So glad you had a great experience at our store. Reviews like this really help our business grow online. We hope we get the pleasure of having you at our store again soon!

reviews.review_text: My girlfriend and I recently made the decision to eat more quality food so we decided to buy a range of seafood options from Daily Catch. We were blown away by the customer service and knowledge of the staff. We ended up getting steak fillets, halibut, tuna and shrimp. Everything was fantastic! My brother owns a seafood restaurant so I am very particular when it comes to seafood and the quality. After the seafood de thawed it had a sweet smell with no  fishyness . I was able to make raw poke with the tuna and it was divine. Would 100% recommend Daily catch and now we place bi weekly orders so daily catch has been crucial towards us leading a healthier lifestyle with amazing seafood! Thank you Daily Catch!

I recently had the opportunity to visit Daily Catch, a retail seafood shop that I had heard great things about. From the moment I walked in, I was impressed with the friendly and attentive customer service I received from the staff. They were more than happy to answer any questions I had about the products and make recommendations based on my preferences. The seafood at Daily Catch is absolutely top-notch. The freshness and quality of the seafood they sell is outstanding. They had variety of species to choose from and were all expertly handled and packaged. I especially enjoyed the local oysters and the fresh sashimi-grade tuna. The prices were very reasonable, and they had good deals on the specials of the day. I also appreciated the shops commitment to sourcing sustainable seafood. Its always good to know that the seafood Im purchasing is not only delicious but also responsibly sourced. Overall, I had an excellent experience at Daily Catch and I would highly recommend it to anyone looking for high-quality and sustainable seafood. The customer service is top-notch and the seafood is outstanding. I will definitely be back!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the Amazing review Chad we can t wait to see you again!

reviews.review_text: Everyone is friendly and helpful. A great selection of fresh seafood. The lobsters, the smoked salmon treats, the freezer stocked with goodies, and other tasty offerings make this place a must when shopping on the Drive. We like to buy a whole salmon and have it filleted and wrapped for our freezer. Yesterday, live Spot Prawns were available. Excellent seafood market!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for the outstanding review John! we work really hard and a hearing this from customers make it all worth while! Look forward to serving you again in the near future! cheers!

reviews.review_text: I am so thrilled to have discovered this little market on the drive. They have incredibly high standards, which means that we get only the best seafood out there. This store is kept so clean and free of clutter, that you just want to spend a lot of time looking around. They have everything from fresh cut fillets, fresh oysters, clams and mussels, to frozen and vacuum packed items done in store. They also have a variety of smoked products that are either frozen or ready to eat. What ever you a looking for, they got it! There are so many things I love about this store, and I hope that more people take a trip down to the Drive to experience what the Daily Catch has to offer.
Went in and ended up getting a whole trout. The cut it up for me and vaccum packed half for my freezer no extra charge. Great service!
We received a delivery from The Daily Catch for the holidays this year and are absolutely blown away by the quality and service. We will be ordering frequently from now on. Thanks.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you so much for the amazing review Robin!! This just made all of our hard work feel totally worth it! look forward to sending you more deliveries in 2022!!!

reviews.review_text: Great place great staff always friendly and amazing bread if you get one

We had gotten 2 Sockeyed Salmons from the island and called The daily Catch to see if they could cut them up for us. They were really fast, great price and amazing service. Love the location. Will totally be going back
Friendly staffs and very enjoyed their sockeye salmon. Super fresh and price was reasonable compare to other options you can get. Highly recommend and I would revisit a couple more times
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the review! we look forward to serving you again!

reviews.review_text: Amazing seafood and great service! They were very helpful with what I needed. I would highly recommend to anyone!

Great prices for the quality, amazing staff, and very helpful owners. I worked here for over three years and the working enviorenment is amazing. The owners Bobby and Ryan understand how to properly run a business. They were never once unfair with their employees and created a great example for leadership. Would 100% reccommend shopping or working here if given the opportunity.

If you re looking for a great place to pick up some fresh seafood, look no further. Their selection of fish is always fresh and the staff are friendly and very helpful. Each time I visit I see delicious new offerings Ive never seen anywhere else, their salmon bacon is amazing! Give them a try, you won t be disappointed.

Wonderful fresh fish and terrific service.  The guys at the Daily catch will portion your fish to your specifications and seal it for the freezer too if you wish.  Nothing but the best.  Superb quality, great variety and amazing service.  They also deliver now too.  Cant be beat!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: thank you for the great review!

reviews.review_text: Just great! I called because of the 100% Sustainable part, and Ill be back because theyre awesome. I know nothing about seafood, and when I called about picking up something on Valentines, the person I spoke to was super helpful, and listed many great options with friendly enthusiasm. They answered all my questions, and encouraged me to come in to see things for myself. So I did, Valentines after work, when I thought they would be slammed/fried/out of everything. Instead, I met Matt, who took time to recommend me his go-to (steelhead), as well as how to cook it -- he added his favourite marinade, gave me the time/temperature/technique, and what touches he likes to add for best flavour. He could not have been nicer or more helpful. It turned out great, was totally delicious, and helped me look good in front of the girl I like...! These guys are great -- Matt for sure. I appreciate them being sustainable, and being so awesome about it. I will be back, I recommend them to everyone, and most of all -- thank them for being great! Theyre awesome -- huge props to Matt -- thank you!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks Jesse! Look forward to seeing you again!

reviews.review_text: This place is great! The food is fresh, the room is clean and the men that work the counters? Well let s just, it s a daily catch alright. From lobster to seasonal spot prawns, you can t go wrong! There is a horseradish that s kick you in the pants good. Did I mention the staff? I did? Oh. Good. This place is a 5/5!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the Amazing review Felicity! Look forward to serving you again soon!

reviews.review_text: Love this place. Just around the block from me. Way better than any supermarket. A couple bucks extra for just a sooo much better experience. The Miso marinated salmon was amazing. I love the staff there as well, you can develop a personal relationship with them because its mostly the same people! They even toss me a discount sometimes :).
reviews.response_from_owner_text: thank you for the great review!

reviews.review_text: EXCELLENT! A great selection of some of the freshest seafood in Vancouver, with a splash of condiments. WE left with a nice selection of fish and my lunch was their Poke, yummy! VISIT next door, Harbour Oyster + Bar, grab some oysters and a nice glass of wine, you will not be disappointed!!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the amazing review Gordon! look forward to serving you again in the future!

reviews.review_text: my go 2 place for quality seafood! Their store has the largest selection of seafood Ive been able to find in Vancouver and the staff are always very friendly and knowledgable. If Im having a busy week i like taking advantage of their online seafood market and ill place an order for delivery. The seafood shows up ice cold and fresh! I cant recommend this place enough. check them out!

The owner Bobby is the man, he and his staff are always very helpful!  Prices are very reasonable for the high quality of products they offer.  Always fresh! Highly recommend!  So happy to have them on the drive!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank You Ari! We look forward to seeing you again soon!

reviews.review_text: Great business run by Bobby and his team! Always the freshest seafood and excellent service. Highly recommend checking them out. Heard great things about their delivery service too. Will have to try it out soon! Thanks guys

Went to grab some halibut for dinner. Price was actually lower than Granville Island, which was surprising given the store being 100% sustainable front to back. I did notice some items were more expensive, but that because they are from a sustainable and ocean wise approved location, as the owner explained to me. I dont mind paying a couple dollars extra to save the environment and grab some super fresh fish!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thanks for the Review

reviews.review_text: Some of the freshest fish I have every had.  As a fish enthusiast and world traveller I always love to try to local catch anywhere I am.  I was blown away by the service and quality at The Daily Catch.  Thanks again, will be back soon!

reviews.review_text: We used them after a fantastic day of fishing with Pacific Angler to process, vacuum pack and freeze our catches. Packaged perfectly for the airline and the fish/gel packs were still frozen when we arrived home in Minnesota! Definitely will use them again!
